snippet.title: Beast Boxing Turbo - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy or Try the Free Demo at http://www.beastboxing.com

Artfully designed first-person boxing game where you punch a turkey in the face. Features a retro-style challenge, character customization, skills to train, and NewGame Plus difficulty modes.

Available November 5th, 2012.

Vote for us at Steam Greenlight! http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=92979562
